# Netlify-only file (ignored by GitHub Pages).
# Belt-and-braces SEO safety on the Netlify mirror: even if the redirect
# above somehow fails, search engines should not index any page served
# from votting-group.netlify.app.

/*
  X-Robots-Tag: noindex, nofollow
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  Permissions-Policy: camera=(), microphone=(), geolocation=()
